description: Data was extracted from TCGA DCC on February 2017. RNAseq gene expression data was generated using UNC V2 pipeline. This table has been deprecated. It has been copied to isb-cgc-bq.TCGA_versioned.RNAseq_hg19_gdc_2017_02. Please see isb-cgc-bq.TCGA.RNAseq_hg19_gdc_current for the most current table.
friendlyName: TCGA HG19 RNASEQ GENE EXPRESSION UNC RSEM 2017 DEPRECATED

fields.description: Project name abbreviation; the program name appended with a project name abbreviation; eg. TCGA-OV, etc.
fields.name: project_short_name

fields.description: Original TCGA case barcode, eg TCGA-12-1089  --  note that each case typically has a primary-tumor sample and a matched-normal (blood or adjacent tissue) sample; please refer to the TCGA Biospecimen table for more details
fields.name: case_barcode

fields.description: Original TCGA sample barcode, eg TCGA-12-1089-01A
fields.name: sample_barcode

fields.description: Original TCGA aliquot barcode, eg TCGA-12-1089-01A-01D-0517-01
fields.name: aliquot_barcode

fields.description: HUGO Gene Nomenclature Committee gene symbol, based on gene_id in original data file, eg AMY1A. Null if no gene symbol could be found (see documentation for additional details regarding ETL) http://isb-cancer-genomics-cloud.readthedocs.io/en/latest/sections/data/data2/ETL_mRNAexpression.html
fields.name: HGNC_gene_symbol

fields.description: The gene symbol. In this table, gene symbol is gene namee.g. ENSG00000251562
fields.name: gene_id

fields.description: Normalized gene expression from original rsem.genes.normalized_results file
fields.name: normalized_count

fields.description: Gene symbol from the original data file, differs if the approved gene symbol has since changed, eg C11orf17 became AKIP1
fields.name: original_gene_symbol

fields.description: Platform used to generate data; either IlluminaHiSeq (for close to 93% of samples) or IlluminaGA
fields.name: platform
